# SOC TYPES AND ROLES 

## SOC 

SOC = security operation center it is a facility where information security team continuosuly monitors and anlyze the securiyt of an orgs. it mainly focuses on DETECT, ANALYSE and RESPOND to cybersec indcidents using tech, ppl and processes.

## TYPES OF SOC 

these types are divided into depeding on securiyt budges : 

### In-House SOC 

it is built and managed by the organization itself. 

### virtual SOC

it works remotely insteed of form one physical location 

### CO-Managed SOC

it combines : Internal securiyt staff + external Security provided (MSSP its a company that provides managed cyber sec services)

### Command SOC

it is a central SOC that supervises mutliple-smaller SOCs across different regions or depts.A central team monitors and coordinates: 

- regional SOCs

- BRanch SOCs

- National security operations

  

